title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Two teen-aged girls preceded me into a supermarket just long enough for me to overhear one of the girls say to the other: “When we went to that party last year we had so much fun it wasn't even funny.” [Submitted by Erik Nappa, Brick, New Jersey.]
